description:
**UPDATED WITH 5 SECOND SOUND!**
Just in time for the Holidays! This app is great for getting festive. It's incredibly intuitive, all you have to do is shake it and hear the jingle bells ring. It's that simple! With tons of fun and a fantastic price, it's a great bargain too! There's no need to bring real bells caroling when you have this handy app!
